---

## skills.sh collection structure

Published as **`shinyobjectz/reactable`** with sub-skills or one bundle:

```
skill/dist/bundle/
  SKILL.md
  VERBS.md              # compiled router
  verbs/
  references/
  dist/registry.json
```

Related skills **linked, not vendored** (hyperframes, gsap) per AGENTS.md open-by-default.

CI: `.github/workflows/skills.yml` on every push → compile + artifact upload.

---

## Agent verb map (progressive disclosure)

| Agent intent | Load | Tools |
|--------------|------|-------|
| New talk | `verbs/decks.md` | — |
| Preview / record | `verbs/stage.md` | native app |
| Fast export | `verbs/post-ffmpeg.md` | ffmpeg |
| Motion post | `verbs/post-hyperframes.md` | hyperframes, gsap |
| YouTube clips | `verbs/youtube.md` | OAuth |
| Setup | `verbs/setup.md` | npm, skills.sh |
| Transcribe / edit speech | `verbs/speech-edit.md` | moonshine, vad |
| Web replay | `verbs/har-blitz.md` | har, blitz |
| Compositing / layouts | `verbs/compositing.md` | ffmpeg, hyperframes |
| DOM camera / cursor | `verbs/camera-dom.md` | gsap, hyperframes |
| Agent synthetic video | `verbs/agent-synthetic.md` | kokoro, stage |
| TTS / shorts voice | `verbs/kokoro-tts.md` | kokoro |
| Local offline agent | `verbs/local-agent.md` | gemma-mlx, nexus |

