## Phase 7 — Local offline agent (Gemma MLX)

| Item | Status |
|------|--------|
| Rust `agent-chat` / `agent-status` / `agent-pull` / `agent-serve` | done | `reactable-tools` → `mlx_lm.server` client |
| gemma-4 backend (mlx_lm.server, uv-pinned, offline) | done | `mlx-community/gemma-4-e4b-it-4bit` |
| Nexus agent loop + sandbox | done | `POST /reactable/agent/chat`; history-safe, symlink-safe |
| Swift agent window | done | `AgentWindow.swift` → `/agent` |
| Bar + tray agent entry | done | robot icon, ⌘L |
| New project (bar/tray/CLI) | done | `ProjectRegistry.createProject`, `projects new` |
| Tests: stub loop/sandbox + real-model e2e | done | `just test-agent-stub` · `just validate-agent-e2e` |
| Token streaming into `/agent` (SSE) | pending | needs nexus SSE passthrough (chat is currently non-stream) |
| Gemma 4 multimodal | pending | vision via mlx-vlm 0.6.4 (`gemma4_unified`) |
| Stage review toolbar + reaction take | pending | record-over-video feedback loop |

Full running/tested/vetted plan → [[docs/GOALS.local-agent]] (gemma-4 mlx_lm.server engine, loop fixes, sandbox vetting, hard e2e).

```bash
reactable agent pull       # one-time model download (no HF account)
reactable agent status     # server-ready | model-cached | needs-pull
# open agent from bar → chat offline
reactable projects new "Hook deck"
```

